Stir of Echoes;;70;;68;;R;;Blue-collar family man Tom Witzky (Kevin Bacon) scoffs at supernatural phenomena -- until he lets his wife's sister, Lisa (Illeana Douglas), put him into a hypnotic trance. Upon waking, Tom realizes he has a psychic connection with his son, Jake (Zachary David Cope). He also has alarming hallucinations of a missing teenage neighbor named Samantha (Jennifer Morrison). Tom, convinced his visions will lead him to the girl, begins a desperate search that puts him into a life-threatening situation.;;Mystery & thriller;;David Koepp;;1999;;Kevin Bacon,Kathryn Erbe,Illeana Douglas,Liza Weil,Kevin Dunn,Conor O'Farrell,Jennifer Morrison,Zachary David Cope,Lisa Lewis,Eddie Bo Smith Jr.,Actor Strus,Stephen Walker,Mary Kay Cook,Larry Neumann;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/stir_of_echoes